        "finding_id": "FIND-GASTRIC-001",
        "domain": "resistance_mechanism",
        "statement": "T-DM1 resistance in HER2-positive gastric cancer is mediated by upregulation of ABC transporters ABCC2 and ABCG2, causing efflux of DM1 payload",
